  "title" : "JPA: export query result to CSV format",
  "body" : "<p>Which is the best way to export a JPA query result in a CSV format?\nI tried opencsv but it wants a java.sql.ResultSet object and I don't understand how to create it. I tried the following code </p>\n\n<pre><code>public ResultSet getAllUsersMap() {\n    String query = \"SELECT p from Participant p ORDER BY p.lastName\";\n    ResultSet rs = (ResultSet) em.createQuery(query).getResultList();\n    return rs;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>but I receive the exception <em>java.lang.ClassCastException: java.util.Vector cannot be cast to java.sql.ResultSet</em></p>\n"
